Name: Chick Rage
About the game: An animator from a local eatery suddenly falls asleep and finds himself in his nightmare, where he is haunted again and again by a ghost, fighting off him with flying discs, he will have to survive in this limbo and be able to wake up! Chick Rage is a top-down arcade game where the game becomes more and more difficult each time, the levels confuse the player more and more, and the ghost gains more and more powers. Run around the location and beat off disks flying everywhere at the enemy, and most importantly, do not stand still! Game Features: -Pixel Art - Increasing Difficulty - Music
